🎮 Breakout Ball Game

A simple and fun arcade-style game where players control a paddle to bounce a ball and break all the bricks.  
The goal is to clear the screen without letting the ball fall!

🚀 Features
- Smooth paddle movement
- Ball and brick collision detection
- Score tracking
- Game over and restart functionality
- Simple and clean graphics

🛠️ Tech Stack
- **Python** (core game logic)
- **Pygame** (graphics and game engine)

🎯 Game Controls
- **Left Arrow (⬅️)** → Move paddle left  
- **Right Arrow (➡️)** → Move paddle right  
- **Q** → Quit the game  

